msgid ""
"Some printers will be automatically detected by Ubuntu; for those that are "
"not, choose &printing;, then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Printer</guimenu>\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t<guimenuitem>Add Printer</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
