msgstr ""
"Avviare <application>Impostazioni servizi</application>: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sistema</guimenu>\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<guisubmenu>Amministrazione</guisubmenu>\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<guimenuitem>Servizi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#: C/partitionsandbooting.xml:152(para) C/internet.xml:117(para)
