"wiki di Ubuntu."

#: C/internet.xml:174(title)
msgid "Web browsing"
msgstr "Esplorare il web"

#: C/internet.xml:175(para)
msgid ""
"The powerful and secure <application>Mozilla Firefox</application> web "
"browser is included in Ubuntu. <application>Firefox</application> features "
"tabbed browsing, pop-up blocking, built-in search, and live bookmarks. Also "
"supported are popular plug-ins such as Java, Macromedia Flash, and "
"RealPlayer. <application>Firefox</application> can be launched by clicking "
"&firefox;."
msgstr ""
"Il potente e sicuro browser web <application>Mozilla Firefox</application> è "
"incluso in Ubuntu. Alcune delle caratteristiche di "
"<application>Firefox</application> comprendono la navigazione a schede, "
"blocco dei pop-up, ricerca integrata e live bookmark. I plug-in più popolari "
"come Java, Macromedia Flash e RealPlayer sono supportati. Per avviare "
"<application>Firefox</application> scegliere &firefox;."

#: C/internet.xml:179(title)
msgid "Viewing Online Audio and Video in Firefox"
msgstr "Visualizzare video e audio online con Firefox"

#: C/internet.xml:180(para)
msgid ""
"To view online audio and video streams in "
"<application>Firefox</application>, you may need to install some plugins. "
"Which plugin you choose to install depends on which media player you prefer "
"(see <xref linkend=\"video\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Per poter vedere i flussi video o ascoltare musica da internet con "
"<application>Firefox</application>, è necessario installare alcuni plug-in. "
"Il plug-in da installare dipende dal tipo di riproduttore multimediale che "
"si utilizza (consultare <xref linkend=\"video\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:182(para)
msgid ""
"For the <application>Totem Gstreamer</application> plugin (the default "
"Ubuntu media player), install the <application>totem-gstreamer-firefox-"
"plugin</application> package from the <quote>Universe</quote> repository "
"(see <xref linkend=\"add-applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Per <application>Totem Gstreamer</application> (il riproduttore multimediale "
"predefinito di Ubuntu), installare il pacchetto <application>totem-gstreamer-"
"firefox-plugin</application> dal repository <quote>Universe</quote> "
"(consultare <xref linkend=\"add-applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:183(para)
msgid ""
"For the <application>Totem Xine</application> plugin, install the "
"<application>totem-xine-firefox-plugin</application> package from the "
"<quote>Universe</quote> repository (see <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Per <application>Totem Xine</application>, installare il pacchetto "
"<application>totem-xine-firefox-plugin</application> dal repository "
"<quote>Universe</quote> (consultare <xref linkend=\"add-applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:184(para)
msgid ""
"For the <application>Mplayer</application> plugin, install the "
"<application>mozilla-mplayer</application> package from the "
"<quote>Multiverse</quote> repository (see <xref linkend=\"add-"
"applications\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Per <application>Mplayer</application>, installare il pacchetto "
"<application>mozilla-mplayer</application> dal repository "
"<quote>Multiverse</quote> (consultare <xref linkend=\"add-applications\"/>)."

#: C/internet.xml:185(para)
msgid ""
"The changes will take effect when you close and open "
"<application>Firefox</application>."
msgstr ""
"I cambiamenti saranno applicati chiudendo e riavviando "
"<application>Firefox</application>."

#: C/internet.xml:187(para)
msgid ""
"These steps will install the plugin for <application>Firefox</application>. "
"However, to play some formats, you may need to add some extra codecs (see "
"<xref linkend=\"codecs\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Questo procedimento serve per installare i plugin per "
"<application>Firefox</application>. Comunque, per riprodurre alcuni formati, "
"è necessario installare dei codec aggiuntivi (consultare <xref "
"linkend=\"codecs\"/>)."

